title: Check warmups
body:
This ticket is to asses the readiness of the warmups.
 The warmups are in https://github.com/AAROC/hackfest-warmups. You should check the following to assess the readiness of the warmups.
  1. [ ] The components you are using have directories in the warmups repo
  1.  [ ] For each component that you are using, there are at least curl examples
